    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Wyrd-draugr are the most powerful and dangerous of the common undead — ancient warriors whose bodies were preserved by Wyrd magic, giving them intelligence, cunning, and command over lesser draugr. Their eyes hold real malice. They carry corroded blades that deal festering necrotic wounds, and can send wyrd-bolts of corruption energy at range. Unlike most undead, wyrd-draugr do not fight to the death — when reduced to nothing, they drop and flee, their Deathless Archive ensuring they survive to return.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
